sub_fields.label: Overwrite Padding
sub_fields.name: overwrite_padding
sub_fields.instructions: Single value for the next blocks top padding

sub_fields.label: Overwrite Margin
sub_fields.name: overwrite_margin
sub_fields.instructions: Comma separated list of 4 values, corresponding to CSS margin format (e.g. 10,0,10,0 for 10px top and bottom)

sub_fields.label: Show Callout?
sub_fields.name: show_callout
sub_fields.message: Show the callout image and text

sub_fields.label: Included Categories
sub_fields.name: included_categories
sub_fields.instructions: Leave blank to include all categories

sub_fields.label: Override Title
sub_fields.name: title
sub_fields.instructions: If no title is entered, default page title will be used

sub_fields.label: Override Image
sub_fields.name: image
sub_fields.instructions: If no image is entered, page featured image will be used

sub_fields.label: Warning
sub_fields.message: For inline videos, please use the "Text" block.
